msgid ""
"Rumor has it a Royal Guard uniform can still be\n"
"found at Hyrule Castle.\n"
"\n"
"Apparently <1.se_co>Riverside Stable<2.re_co> has a copy of\n"
"Super Rumor Mill EX, which details some\n"
"rumors about this rare outfit."
msgstr ""

