msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt04_Finish"
msgid ""
"You found the <1.se_co>royal guard uniform<2.re_co> from treasure\n"
"chests in the hidden room near the dining hall,\n"
"the storage space in the guards' chamber,\n"
"and on the second floor of the castle.\n"
"\n"
"Believing those rumors really paid off!"
msgstr ""

