msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt04_Step01"
msgid ""
"You read Super Rumor Mill EX: Volume 4!\n"
"According to this special issue, Hyrule Castle\n"
"still houses a uniform once belonging to the\n"
"royal guards who protected the royal family.\n"
"It can supposedly be found in treasure chests\n"
"hidden near the <1.se_co>dining hall<2.re_co>, in the <3.se_co>guards'\n"
"chamber<4.re_co>, and on the <5.se_co>second floor<6.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"If you believe the rumors, try to find the\n"
"hidden treasure!\n"
"Treasure chests remaining: <7.se_co><8.va><9.re_co>"
